editor_description = "PLACEHOLDER — leave empty in source control. Instance the external Blender diorama here (e.g. res://art/title/title_diorama.glb or .tscn): sea, sun + halo, sun-glint water facets, longship, mead hall + pennant, mountains. Do NOT rebuild these as Godot BoxMesh/PrismMesh/QuadMesh primitives — all 3D assets are authored in Blender and imported. The water-glint and banner-flag shaders in this folder are for materials on that imported asset."

